OL,3,CTfL to regulate pedicabs as thousands
OL,4,Cof Londoners express safety concerns
OL,6,FA new report shows overwhelming public
OL,7,Fsupport for tighter regulation - with
OL,8,Fmost Londoners saying they feel unsafe
OL,9,Fusing them, as Antoine Allen reports
OL,11,FPlans to regulate the use of pedicabs
OL,12,Fin London are set to advance next
OL,13,Fyear, following a consultation that
OL,14,Fhas found overwhelming support for
OL,15,Ftougher safety standards.
OL,17,FThe consultation, carried out by
OL,18,FTransport for London (TfL) found that
OL,19,Fout of nearly 7,700 respondents, 75%
OL,20,Fcurrently felt unsafe while using a
OL,21,Fpedicab in the capital.
