OL,6,FThe rickshaws, common sights in
OL,7,FLondon's main tourist destinations,
OL,8,Fare not currently regulated.
OL,10,FNearly all (97%) of participants
OL,11,Fbacked mandatory insurance for pedicab
OL,12,Foperators, 95% support the
OL,13,Fintroduction of criminal background
OL,14,Fchecks for drivers, and 85% believe
OL,15,Fthat pedicab fares are too expensive.
