OL,3,CTfL to regulate pedicabs as thousands
OL,4,Cof Londoners express safety concerns
OL,6,FDraft policy proposals include a TfL
OL,7,Flicensing system, along the same lines
OL,8,Fas that currently in place for London
OL,9,Ftaxi drivers, with requirements
OL,10,Fincluding a minimum age of 18, a UK or
OL,11,FEEA-valid drivers' licence, and
OL,12,FEnglish language skills.
OL,14,FTfL are also considering the
OL,15,Fintroduction of insurance
OL,16,Frequirements, alongside safety
OL,17,Fequipment mandates.
