OL,3,CTfL to regulate pedicabs as thousands
OL,4,Cof Londoners express safety concerns
OL,6,FThe proposals could come into force
OL,7,Ffrom 2026 ` but will become more
OL,8,Fdetailed over the coming months, and
OL,9,Fare subject to a second consultation
OL,10,Fat the end of the year.
OL,12,FThe use of music by pedicab drivers
OL,13,Fsparked particular frustration among
OL,14,Fthe survey's respondents ` including
OL,15,Fover 2,400 comments, double the number
OL,16,Frelating to any other topic.
