OL,3,CTfL to regulate pedicabs as thousands
OL,4,Cof Londoners express safety concerns
OL,6,F96% of participants were in favour of
OL,7,Fvolume limitations on music and other
OL,8,Faudio from pedicabs, and 78% believe
OL,9,Fthese controls should be in place "all
OL,10,Fthe time".
OL,12,FHelen Chapman, TfL's director of
OL,13,FLicensing & Regulation, said:
OL,14,F"Pedicabs can provide a unique and
OL,15,Fgreen way to see the capital.
OL,17,F"However, they have an impact on the
OL,18,Fsafety of the road network and are
OL,19,Fcurrently unregulated.
