OL,3,CTfL to regulate pedicabs as thousands
OL,4,Cof Londoners express safety concerns
OL,6,F"We look forward to working with the
OL,7,Fpedicab industry to ensure it is run
OL,8,Ffairly and safely and continues to be
OL,9,Fa sustainable mode of transport."
OL,11,FThe move comes in the wake of
OL,12,Fparliamentary calls for regulation
OL,13,Flast year ` which culminated in the
OL,14,FPedicabs (London) Act, granting TfL
OL,15,Fthe statutory powers necessary to go
OL,16,Fthrough with the licensing system.
