OL,3,CTfL to regulate pedicabs as thousands
OL,4,Cof Londoners express safety concerns
OL,6,FThe transport authority proposes to
OL,7,Ftake the lead on enforcement of any
OL,8,Fnew regulations themselves, with all
OL,9,Fexpenses recouped through the fees for
OL,10,Fpedicab licences.
OL,12,FIn a campaign response to the survey,
OL,13,Fthe London Pedicab Welfare Association
OL,14,F(LPWA) said: "While the intention
OL,15,Fbehind this requirement is to ensure
OL,16,Fthe safety of passengers and regulate
OL,17,Fthe industry, it has created
OL,18,Fchallenges for pedicab drivers who do
OL,19,Fnot possess a driving licence."
