OL,6,FThe LPWA instead proposed
OL,7,Falternatives, including the
OL,8,Fintroduction of a theory test for
OL,9,Fdrivers to obtain their licence.
OL,11,FRos Morgan, chief executive at the
OL,12,FHeart of London Business Alliance,
OL,13,Fwelcomed the proposals, saying: "For
OL,14,Ffar too long, members of the public
OL,15,Fhave been at the mercy of rogue
OL,16,Foperators who do nothing to enhance
OL,17,Fthe reputation of the West End.
OL,19,F"Implementation of the scheme could
OL,20,Fnot come soon enough."
